{"pageProps":{"bookPath":"leetcode","postPath":"lc-buy-stock","post":{"title":"买卖股票的最佳时机","body":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\">目录</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\">\n<li><a href=\"#_暴力法\">暴力法</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_dp法\">DP法</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"preamble\">\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/best-time-to-buy-and-sell-stock/\">121. 买卖股票的最佳时机</a>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>为讨论方便，约定输入数组为 <code>prices</code>，数组长度为 <code>n</code>，前 <code>i+1</code> 项构成的子列记为 <code>prices[0,i]</code>。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_暴力法\">暴力法</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>我们对所有的 <code>prices[i]</code> 和 <code>prices[j]</code> 构成的有序对做处理（其中 <code>j &gt; i</code>）。如果 <code>prices[j] &gt; prices[i]</code>，\n说明有盈利，就记录 <code>prices[j] - prices[i]</code> 的值，求出所有的这个差，就其中最大的那个，就是答案了。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number[]}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">prices</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> maxProfit = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"hljs-params\">prices</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> result = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; prices.length; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> j = i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; j &lt; prices.length; j++) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(prices[j] &gt; prices[i]) {\n                result = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(prices[j] - prices[i], result);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> result;\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这肯定是一个 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n^2)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 的算法，不过空间复杂度是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(1)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_dp法\">DP法</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>我们考虑所有形如 <code>prices[0,i]</code> 的子列。对于每一个这样的子列，我们求出这个子列的最小值，记这个最小值构成的序列为\n<code>dp</code>（提前暴露了）。例如，如果 <code>prices = [7, 1, 5, 3, 6, 4]</code>，那么 <code>dp = [7, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1]</code>。然后，我们对\n<code>prices</code> 从第 2 项（也就是 <code>prices[1]</code>）开始往后，对每个 <code>prices[i]</code>\n做处理，如果 <code>prices[i] &gt; dp[i-1]</code>，就记录 <code>prices[i] - dp[i-1]</code>，最后求这个差的最大值。这个最大值就是最大收益。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>求 <code>dp</code> 数列的话，思路就很简单了，<code>dp[i] = min(dp[i-1], prices[i])</code>，就这样。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>沿着这个思路，可以写出下面的代码：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number[]}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">prices</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> maxProfit = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">prices</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> dp = [prices[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>]]\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; prices.length; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> p = prices[i];\n        dp[i] = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(p, dp[i<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>])\n    }\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> result = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; prices.length; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> p = prices[i];\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (p &gt; dp[i<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>]) {\n            result = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(result, p - dp[i<span class=\"hljs-number\">-1</span>])\n        }\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> result\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这段代码的时间复杂度是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>，空间复杂度也是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>（因为使用了一个额外的 <code>dp</code> 数组）。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>我们观察这段代码，发现使用了两个完全一样的 <code>for</code> 循环，在第二个 <code>for</code> 循环中，对每个 <code>i</code>，我们只关心 <code>dp[i-1]</code>，这暗示我们可以把\n<code>dp</code> 数组都给省了。改造后的代码如下：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number[]}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">prices</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> maxProfit = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"hljs-params\">prices</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dpi_1 = prices[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>];\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> result = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; prices.length; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> p = prices[i];\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (p &gt; dpi_1) {\n            result = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(result, p - dpi_1);\n        }\n        dpi_1 = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(p, dpi_1);\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> result;\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这样优化之后，空间复杂度就是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(1)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 了。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","type":"adoc"},"book":{"title":"LeetCode","toc":[{"title":"53. 最大子数组","path":"lc-maximum-subarray"},{"title":"62. 不同路径","path":"lc-unique-paths"},{"title":"63. 不同路径 II","path":"lc-unique-paths-ii"},{"title":"64. 最小路径和","path":"lc-minimum-path-sum"},{"title":"70. 爬楼梯","path":"lc-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"95. 不同的二叉搜索树 II","path":"lc-unique-binary-search-trees-ii"},{"title":"121. 买卖股票","path":"lc-buy-stock"},{"title":"132. 分割回文串 II","path":"lc-palindrome-partitioning-ii"},{"title":"198. 打家劫舍","path":"lc-house-robber"},{"title":"276. 栅栏涂色","path":"lc-paint-fence"},{"title":"303. 区域和检索 - 数组不可变","path":"lc-range-sum-query-immutable"},{"title":"746. 使用最小花费爬楼梯","path":"lc-min-cost-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"146. LRU 缓存机制","path":"lc-lru-cache"},{"title":"数完全二叉树节点","path":"lc-count-complete-tree-nodes"}],"path":"leetcode"}},"__N_SSG":true}